# SQLite database files
# If you are using a local SQLite database for development, ignore its file(s).
# The default name is often db.sqlite3, but adjust as needed.
*.sqlite 
*.sqlite3
*.db
# Does this cover Postgresql? Not really, as Postgresql typically runs as a separate service.
/database.db # or the specific name of your db file
db.sqlite3-journal

